==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*πυρέσσω / puressō / poo-res'-so
*From [[πυρά]] {{GG|4443}}; to be on fire, that is, (specifically) to have a fever: 

===Verb===
'''πυρέσσω'''

# be sick of a fever.

